						               													<description>Rule book:&amp;#10;'A set of games with novel Bingo variants for 2-8 players.&amp;#10;Idea of the game:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Casino Royal presents the sparkling world of the big, international casinos in your own home. You experience a truly regal pastime with this interesting set of novel, thrilling Poker and Bingo variants. Casino Roal offers variety and fresh entertainment over and over again.'&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Contents:&amp;#10;- 8 boards each showing 20 card pictures&amp;#10;- a pack of 52 playing cards&amp;#10;- 160 green chips&amp;#10;- 40 yellow chips&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Three games:&amp;#10;- Casino Royal Poker: 52 playing cards turning up one by one. Each player puts a chip on the corresponding card value on his board. When a player reachs a (high) poker combination he can decide to bet. The one with the highest combination wins the bet.&amp;#10;- Bluff-Poker Variante: each player receives three cards. All the players bet. Once this betting is concluded the dealer begins to turn up and call out the remaining card and the players put a chip on each of the card pictures shown on their bords. When a player reachs a (high) poker combination with the cards and his board he can decide to call out 'No more bets'. The highest card combination wins the bet.&amp;#10;- Casino Royal Bingo: the cards are called out one by one. The players put a chip on the card pictures on their board. A player wins when he can form a predetermined formation on his board (a row or a T, H....). he wins all the chips on the boards of the other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
